载的方式提升任务执行的一致性与可复用性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968384\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5898148148148148\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4185cab7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE4fA9TAMRQwVRF8SIDCLNn3L9jibGQNM2RRcV0tPF2q3T4cZMNzwEyrAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌2025 年最佳 SEO 学习路线和书籍列表推荐</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://bysocket.com/best-seo-books-in-2025/\" target=\"_blank\">https://bysocket.com/best-seo-books-in-2025/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文提出了一个三步走的SEO学习路线，强调以基础打牢、动手实践和持续升级为核心，通过两条路径（自学资源和官方文档）以及三大类优质博客来保持前沿，并给出可交流的人物圈与资源，帮助读者在 AI 时代持续提升SEO能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968387\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4925925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1920\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2639cc49&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE4WpSlqib3iaXZyDjBh67BNtzxCc38DrPp6Jd0gRBoBeL2oP5jT07lGdhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌B端怎么梳理场景？产品方案怎么设计？</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4NDYwNDc2MA==&amp;mid=2247491354&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=746e1e125d1db6cbc25480e211b5bf7d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/txVYPcXQXQxCCSULhV_F_g\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/txVYPcXQXQxCCSULhV_F_g</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文围绕 B 端产品经理在设计产品方案时如何通过科学的需求分析和场景梳理，确保方案覆盖核心业务流程、完整的业务场景，以及可落地的系统与业务方案。提出以业务为驱动的设计思路，强调从梳理核心流程入手，逐步展开场景描述，最终通过跨行业与同行借鉴来设计可落地的方案。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌复杂任务AI处理实践：淘宝工程师的实战手记</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650541986&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b6fd90b2a69aa47bbf1b5c3e5f0200c8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/HmXRwrLrjEXiHVzZHToXeg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/HmXRwrLrjEXiHVzZHToXeg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文系统性总结了将人类重复性工作抽象为“感知-决策-执行”的 AI 闭环的实践经验与方法论，围绕“眼睛、手、脑”三要素的工具化实现、两种主流工作模式（Workflow 与 Agent）以及多层次的AI效果保障，展示从工具助手到智能体的演进路径，并通过若干真实场景案例说明AI在数据治理、工单排查、存储治理等复杂场景中的应用边界与实际效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968386\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.197\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1000\" width=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37aaa742&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE4vu1E6lMlcKYxbHQ2yPv8XvKPEiaFf5KHScbU5ia4HBjLj6W9RhkJpyWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌策略产品权重设计方法连载：优序图法，AHP，熵值法，CRITIC，独立性权重，信息量权重，主观成分分析法，因子分析法</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3Mjg1MjQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2452455446&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b8df0b5d3f0462869e2caf2b765ead92&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LcTd8N3GRmPsRS3eIjKKjg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LcTd8N3GRmPsRS3eIjKKjg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文系统梳理了在策略产品分发中用于设定特征权重的8种主流方法，并将其分为四大类：基于主观判断的权重法（AHP、优序图法）、基于信息量的客观法（熵值法）、基于数据波动与相关性的客观法（CRITIC、独立性权重、信息量权重）以及基于信息浓缩的降维法（因子分析、主成分法）。文章强调权重的来源决定了适用场景，指出在数据充足与需要降低主观偏见时偏向客观法；在数据不足但存在明确业务共识时可采用主观法。最后提出结合业务目标选择权重方法的重要性，并预告后续将逐一讲解各方法的原理、步骤与避坑点。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌推荐系统三十年：从协同过滤到大模型时代的技术编年史</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&amp;mid=2247693496&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=9dfc0086b64a9d595772bf76de65f1c0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XgNig9a0M8CthA561Ie-Yg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XgNig9a0M8CthA561Ie-Yg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文以时间为轴梳理了推荐系统从起源到大模型时代的技术演进，聚焦协同过滤、矩阵分解、深度学习及生成式大模型在实际应用中的关键突破、典型系统与产业实践，并对未来趋势与落地挑战给出洞察，强调混合架构、端到端生成、序列建模与工程化落地的重要性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968385\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb0cebd6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE4VxeQVsly