ps://tenten.co/learning/nano-banana-pro-tutorials/</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Nano-Banana Pro 是基於 Gemini 3 Pro 的專業級圖像生成與編輯模型，擁有高精細構圖、穩定風格鎖定與高解析輸出能力，適用於商業級素材與跨場景視覺管理；要充分發揮其價值，關鍵在於以創意導演的完整創意簡報與清晰的主體、場景、光線、情緒與用途描述進行互動與微調，並善用多參考圖進行 Identity Locking，從而在資訊圖、2D/3D 應用、廣告分鏡與品牌視覺中穩定產出高品質資產。官方與社群工具整合（如 Gemini API、Google AI Studio 等）使工作流程更順暢，將 AI 視為團隊的視覺製作夥伴，而非僅是概念工具。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968388\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55859375\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" width=\"1024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4529a3ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE47YIic2eMg3ic2IpBxlA4FpsMPOibaS0GzphBIGNuSUIStQTp3VQOPAickw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 48px 8px 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 65px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b74e1aca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoloQt5Gibu37EDyzwasmLC9Ld1Z8ia20TCibPO3Vjh9BB9sKKsPwq4k26g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot