dth:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌WinDog(赢多)：为用户构建属于自己量化交易系统！</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/windyson/WinDog\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/windyson/WinDog</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">赢多交易系统————股票量化机器人交易系统。 目前已经实现：多策略自动选股，自动控制仓位，自动完成买卖交易，自动计算盈利情况。并根据执行不同选股策略的机器人表现进行优选，找到当前最有效的策略，为用户自己操盘提供参考。机器人实时操盘指令，可通过企业微信推送到群，方便用户及时了解市场行情。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968391\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1595\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6250bd32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE4xEOhK95zC5yn1PqhPrvSXVWsFloeyBiaIzXGiaRpISwQcuKib31VVcNWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;\">▌AI股票大师</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/hengruiyun/AI-Stock-Master\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hengruiyun/AI-Stock-Master</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个基于AI 的股票趋势分析平台，经过AI 大模型解读中国、香港、美国股票市场，融合多种核心算法：RTSI个股趋势强度指数、MSCI市场情绪指数和核心强势分析器，为投资者提供全方位的投资决策支持。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968389\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7114427860696517\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1005\" width=\"1005\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=271148a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2RRGBVtoskrkXibZoulBRHE4qEykIdBbBHAkDz6ibUnricwTVdwTosapMcyGqoiaCw0PFK5lj4DpibQBwQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
